[src:doxygen/commands-p02] Alternatively, one `\test` command may mention several test cases.
[src:doxygen/commands-p02] The `\test` command ends when a blank line or some other sectioning command is encountered.
[src:doxygen/commands-p02] The description will also add an item to a separate Test list and the two instances of the description will be cross-referenced.
[src:doxygen/commands-p02] Each item in the Test list will be preceded by a header that indicates the origin of the item.
[src:doxygen/commands-p02] The Test list and the corresponding entries can be disabled by setting the GENERATE_TESTLIST to NO.
[src:doxygen/commands-p02] Starts a paragraph where one or more todo items are described.
[src:doxygen/commands-p02] Multiple adjacent `\todo` commands will be joined into a single paragraph.
